'''泰坦蚺屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Titanoboa''，意即「極大的蚺蛇」）<ref name="head">{{cite journal|last=Head|first=Jason J.|coauthors=Jonathan I. Bloch, Alexander K. Hastings, Jason R. Bourque, Edwin A. Cadena, Fabiany A. Herrera, P. David Polly, and Carlos A. Jaramillo|title=Giant boid snake from the paleocene neotropics reveals hotr past equatorial temperatures.|url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v457/n7230/abs/nature07671.html|journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]]|volume=457|pages=715–718|accessdate=2009-02-05|archive-date=2017-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170307085206/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v457/n7230/abs/nature07671.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一個生活在[[古新世|古新世]]（約 6,000 至 5,800 萬年前）[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]東北部[[瓜希拉省|瓜希拉省]]的無毒、肉食性[[蚺|蚺]]类。<ref name=Nature>{{cite web | title = Scientists find world's biggest snake | url = http://www.nature.com/news/2009/090204/full/news.2009.80.html | date = 4 February 2009 | accessdate = 4 February 2009 | first = Roberta | last = Kwok | publisher = ''[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]]'' | archive-date = 2019-09-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190907223226/http://www.nature.com/news/2009/090204/full/news.2009.80.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>已知的唯一種'''塞雷洪泰坦蚺'''（''T. cerrejonensis''）也是已知最大的蛇。<ref name=Nature/>把它[[化石|石化]]的[[脊椎骨|脊椎骨]]與現代蛇比較，研究人員估計其最大全長 14 米（46 英呎），體重超過 1,100 公斤（2,400 磅），身體最粗處厚達 1 米（3.3 英呎）。<ref name=Nature/>它可能是以[[鱷魚|鱷魚]]為食的。<ref name=CTV>{{cite web | url = http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/20090204/snake_biggest_090204/20090204?hub=SciTech | title = CTV: Ancient, gargantuan snakes ate crocs for breakfast | publisher = [[CTV電視網|CTV電視網]] | date = February 4, 2009 | accessdate = 4 February 2009 | archive-date = 2009-02-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090206074337/http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/20090204/snake_biggest_090204/20090204?hub=SciTech | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

