==發現==
二十八條巨蚺的化石是在2009年在[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]北部的[[塞雷洪煤礦|塞雷洪煤礦]]被發現的。<ref name=head/><ref name=Nature/>在此以前，在[[南美洲|南美洲]]昔日的熱帶地區很少有古新世的脊椎動物被發現。<ref>{{cite web | title = Fossil of 43-foot super snake Titanoboa found in Colombia | url = http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-sci-snake5-2009feb05,0,6550292.story | publisher = [[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] | first = Thomas H. | last = Maugh II | date = 4 February 2009 | accessdate = 4 February 2009 | archive-date = 2009-02-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090206170819/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-sci-snake5-2009feb05,0,6550292.story | dead-url = no }}</ref>

此種是由一隊由[[佛羅里達大學|佛羅里達大學]]研究脊椎動物的[[古生物學|古生物學]]家約納森·希洛克（Jonathan Bloch）和[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]][[史密森尼熱帶研究所|史密森尼熱帶研究所]]的[[古植物學|古植物學]]家卡洛斯·哈拉米約（Carlos Jaramillo）率領的國際科學考察隊伍發現的。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2009/02/090204112217.htm | title = At 2,500 Pounds And 43 Feet, Prehistoric Snake Is Largest On Record | publisher = [[科學日報|科學日報]] | date = February 4, 2009 | accessdate = 4 February 2009 | archive-date = 2017-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170811060641/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2009/02/090204112217.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==體型與溫度的關係==
由於蛇是環溫動物，這項發現也暗示了，當時的其生活的熱帶地區比研究人員原先估計的更溫暖，平均氣溫為 32℃（90°F）。<ref name=head/><ref name=Nature/><ref name=NPR>{{cite web | title = 1-Ton Snakes Once Slithered In The Tropics | url = http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=100262412 | date = 5 February 2009 | accessdate = 5 February 2009 | first = Christopher | last = Joyce | publisher = [[全國公共廣播電台|全國公共廣播電台]] | archive-date = 2019-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190107203119/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=100262412 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6V6R-47S6RC4-3&_user=10&_rdoc=1&_fmt=&_orig=search&_sort=d&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=f53378580e88505b71158a35999e10ef |title=Science Direct: Climate model sensitivity to atmospheric CO2 levels in the Early–Middle Paleogene |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208021148/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6V6R-47S6RC4-3&_user=10&_rdoc=1&_fmt=&_orig=search&_sort=d&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=f53378580e88505b71158a35999e10ef |dead-url=no }}</ref>只有這樣的氣候才能讓蛇長得這麼大。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://journals.royalsociety.org/content/p30384h277127964/ |title=The Royal Society: Gigantism, temperature and metabolic rate in terrestrial poikilotherms |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202073212/http://journals.royalsociety.org/content/p30384h277127964/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/video/?slug=la-sci-snake5-2009feb05-vid |title=AP: Video of Titanoboa |accessdate=2009-02-06 |archive-date=2009-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208020249/http://www.latimes.com/video/?slug=la-sci-snake5-2009feb05-vid |dead-url=no }}</ref>而目前當地的年平均氣溫為 28℃。<ref>{{cite news
